<article class="prose">
  <h1>About Planet WriteLog</h1>
  <p>
    Planet WriteLog is a community aggregator for the
    <a href="https://mmsmoa.com" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft Management Summit (MMS)</a>
    community. It surfaces new blog posts, GitHub releases, and YouTube videos from MVPs and
    presenters — linking directly to their content, never republishing it.
  </p>

  <h2>How to add yourself</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>
      Fork <a href="https://github.com/leghammer-git/planet-writelog">the repository</a>
      on GitHub.
    </li>
    <li>
      Create a new file <code>people/{your-handle}.json</code> following the schema below.
      Your handle must be lowercase alphanumeric + hyphens and match the filename.
    </li>
    <li>
      Open a pull request. CI will validate your JSON against the schema automatically.
      Once merged, you'll appear in the feed within the hour.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Person file schema</h2>
  <pre><code>{
  "name": "Your Name",
  "handle": "your-handle",
  "pronouns": "they/them",          // optional
  "title": "MVP · Endpoint Management",
  "bio": "One or two sentences.",
  "avatar": "https://...",           // optional; falls back to GitHub avatar
  "links": {
    "website": "https://...",
    "github": "your-handle",
    "bluesky": "you.bsky.social",
    "mastodon": "@you@infosec.exchange",
    "linkedin": "your-linkedin-slug"
  },
  "feeds": [
    { "type": "blog",            "url": "https://yourblog.com/feed.xml" },
    { "type": "github-releases", "repo": "your-handle/your-repo" },
    { "type": "youtube",         "channel_id": "UCxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx" }
  ]
}</code></pre>

  <h2>Feed types</h2>
  <dl>
    <dt><code>blog</code></dt>
    <dd>Any RSS 2.0 or Atom feed URL.</dd>
    <dt><code>github-releases</code></dt>
    <dd>GitHub releases Atom feed for a repo you maintain (<code>owner/repo</code>).</dd>
    <dt><code>youtube</code></dt>
    <dd>Your YouTube channel ID (starts with <code>UC</code>). Find it in YouTube Studio → Settings → Channel → Advanced.</dd>
  </dl>

  <h2>Have questions?</h2>
  <p>
    Open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/leghammer-git/planet-writelog/issues">GitHub</a>.
  </p>
</article>
